data.description: Experience the ultimate mountain living in this ranch retreat nestled in the picturesque town of Florissant! With 5 acres of land, this fantastic property offers breathtaking views of Pikes Peak that will leave you in awe. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly integrates the beauty of the outdoors with the comfort of the indoors. The expansive windows and multiple walk-outs provide an abundance of natural light and allow you to immerse yourself in the surrounding natural splendor. The living, dining, and kitchen areas feature real hardwood floors enhanced with a wood burning fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen includes top-of-the-line appliances, a grand center island, and abundant storage space. The primary retreat offers a spacious walk-in closet with custom organization and ensuite bathroom with dual sinks and walk-in tiled shower. The partially finished walk-out basement boasts a generously sized recreation area that provides ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Make use of additional bedrooms and a 1/2 bathroom with heated floors that can be upgraded to a full bathroom in the future. The unfinished space provides ample storage space or room to grow. The exterior of the home is adorned with stunning cedar siding, adding a touch of rustic charm. Enjoy the soothing sounds of a water feature and take advantage of the ample deck space, perfect for outdoor gatherings and admiring the panoramic views. An inviting hot tub area allows you to unwind while soaking in the beauty of your surroundings. A year-round creek gracefully flows through the property, adding a touch of tranquility. With county maintained roads, you'll have easy access to the property year-round, ensuring a convenient and hassle-free lifestyle!
